    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Frames of parallel metal bars used for broiling food over coals or an open fire.  Also, wood gratings or racks for the same purpose.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
